{"arkId":"cl010278509","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010278509","modified ":"2026-01-17","title":"statue","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"statue (fragment, t\u00eate)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : romain imp\u00e9rial\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Ie s. ap. J.-C. (?) (1 - 100)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":true,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1,"endYear":100,"imprecision":"","text":"Ie s. ap. J.-C. (?)","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AGRR 2","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"Ma 5029","type":"Num\u00e9ro catalogue"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"original grec ; 2e quart Ve s. av. J.-C.","printState":"","description":"philosophe (?, portrait, cheveux, court, barbe)\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : Il manque le nez, l\u0027\u00e9paule droite, et une partie de l\u0027avant du buste. La surface est us\u00e9e.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"37","displayDimension":"37 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"25","displayDimension":"25 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"23","displayDimension":"23 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : marbre (marbre grec)\r\nTechnique : ronde-bosse (sculpture)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Historique de la base \u0022R\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique (MNR Rose-Valland)\u0022 : \r\nD\u0027apr\u00e8s les recherches men\u00e9es jusqu\u0027\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent, l\u0027historique de cette oeuvre reste inconnu avant guerre. Elle a \u00e9t\u00e9 acquise, pendant l\u0027Occupation, par la Glyptoth\u00e8que de Munich chez Mikas, antiquaire \u00e0 Paris (alors au 3, rue Solf\u00e9rino, VIIe). Selon un fichier de la commission de r\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique, elle a \u00e9t\u00e9 retrouv\u00e9e au d\u00e9p\u00f4t du monast\u00e8re de Reisach, pr\u00e8s d\u0027Oberaudorf, en Allemagne, sur la fronti\u00e8re autrichienne. Sa valeur est alors estim\u00e9e \u00e0 1250 RM (1) et (2). Cette t\u00eate masculine a \u00e9t\u00e9 ramen\u00e9e au Central Collecting Point de Munich le 15 novembre 1946 (num\u00e9ro de Munich 40286\/Degerndorf 9). La \u0022Property card\u0022 indique \u0022Identifying Marks : Skatr. [?] Inv. N\u00b0 310, Glypt. Inv. N\u00b0 530\u0022 (2). Cit\u00e9e dans le r\u00e9pertoire des restitutions de la zone am\u00e9ricaine en 1947 (3), elle est rapatri\u00e9e vers la commission de r\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique \u00e0 Paris par le quinzi\u00e8me (ou quinzi\u00e8me bis ?) convoi en provenance de Munich, le 7 janvier 1947 (sous le num\u00e9ro 393 ; num\u00e9ro fran\u00e7ais 10685) (4). Propos\u00e9e \u00e0 la premi\u00e8re commission de choix des oeuvres de la r\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique du 27 octobre 1949 (5), l\u0027oeuvre est attribu\u00e9e aux mus\u00e9es nationaux (mus\u00e9e du Louvre, d\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques et romaines) en 1951 (6). Une d\u00e9charge sign\u00e9e par Georges Salles le 9 novembre 1949 atteste de son arriv\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e du Louvre (7).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"attribution par l\u0027office des biens et int\u00e9r\u00eats priv\u00e9s (MNR)","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Mus\u00e9es Nationaux R\u00e9cup\u00e9ration","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"attribution par l\u0027office des biens et int\u00e9r\u00eats priv\u00e9s (MNR)"}],"denomination":[{"value":"statue"},{"value":"fragment"},{"value":"t\u00eate"}],"material":[{"value":"marbre"}],"technic":[{"value":"ronde-bosse"}],"description":[{"value":"barbe"},{"value":"cheveux"},{"value":"portrait"},{"value":"philosophe"},{"value":"court"}],"originalObject":[{"value":"original grec"},{"value":"2e quart Ve s. av. J.-C."}],"period":[{"value":"romain imp\u00e9rial"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828204_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828204_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Herv\u00e9 Lewandowski","type":"face, recto, avers, avant","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828189_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828189_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Herv\u00e9 Lewandowski","type":"dessus","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828201_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828201_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Herv\u00e9 Lewandowski","type":"d\u00e9tail","position":2},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828202_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000278509\/0000828202_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Herv\u00e9 Lewandowski","type":"d\u00